race.comment: ASTON GOZO (6) was strongly fancied last time but finished second (34.96), beaten 1.2 lengths. Deserves serious consideration. REANNA'S PRIDE (2) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start seventh (29.96) at this track. Solid record at the distance winning three races. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Key player if finds best. DESIRABILITY (7) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 595m (35.05). Should be in this for a long way. BEST FOR LAST (8) is one of the chances after a minor prize in quick time last start.
